lieing is like a disease. it consumes you. until you cant stop. it just goes on forever, and ever, and everyone knows your a lier.

It is hard to explain who i am. I am a very depressed child. well i should say young adult right?&nbsp;
I like to put on a front, a happy joking little front that amuses most people, i let them laugh it up and i along with them get some enjoyment. BUt like EVERYONE i hide things. but i want to let you know what i have hidden for so long.

i cut myself when i got depressed. i wouldn't find a razor blade to slide across my skin... i would scratch myself and just take off the top skin or i would gouge my skin or i would create a scaring desighn, i still have the scars on my arm and on both my legs. and sometimes when i get really worked up i want to do it again, and sometimes i do, but not like i used to.&nbsp;

I also have a tendancy to act like a whore. a complete and total whore. its&nbsp;a depressing scene to watch, my simple self searching for love and throwing myself at men to make myself feel beautiful. but the worst part is, is i realize all of it.. and it dosen't matter at all. i still do it.&nbsp;





okay i feel better now. just had to get it off my chest, maybe i can sleep now!
